# Admin Automation

- Admin is designed for 1-person operation first, expandable to role-based teams later.
- Normal cases should be automated; Admin should focus on exception queues.
- Every manual Admin action requires a reason and audit log.
- High-risk operations require confirmation and appropriate permissions.
- Kill switches must be simple, visible, and auditable.
